alldsplusclimate.mat: climate variables for the 246 languages in the IDS+
data set

dictis.mat: climate variables for the 53 languages in the dictionary data set

twitterclimate.mat: climate variables for the 45 languages in the full
twitter data set

These variables were extracted from latlong.mat, which includes climate
invormation associated with glottolog and iso language codes. The data in
latlong.mat are based on files downloaded from glottolog.

Urban areas:

urbanareas2010.txt was downloaded from

http://www2.census.gov/geo/docs/maps-data/data/gazetteer/2013_Gazetteer/2013_Gaz_ua_national.zip



